## 🧩 How It Works

### 1. **Floating Balls**
JavaScript spawns a random sports ball every 1.8 seconds.  
Each ball:
- animates upward  
- rotates  
- fades out  
- triggers the touchdown sound  

### 2. **Product Cards**
Cards are manually added to the `.product-grid` section in `index.html`.  
Each card follows this structure:

```html
<article class="product-card">
  <img src="IMAGE_URL" alt="DESCRIPTION">
  <h3>Product Title</h3>
  <p class="price">C$0.00</p>
  <a href="EBAY_LINK" target="_blank" class="btn">View on eBay</a>
</article>


